# Once program is launched,
# the main UI should appear and be empty.
#
# In order to add first transaction,
# click on the plus in the top right corner.
#
# Name and Price fields must be specified
# in order to save transaction, 
# program will not allow user to save unless fields
# have been filled out.
#
# Once a transaction has been saved the home
# UI will update with the transaction listed
# and the total running balance will update too.
#
# All transaction records are clickable on the home
# page to view more information.
#
# In order to delete a transaction, user must swipe
# right on the transaction on the homepage then
# click delete.
